text: Hertha Rosmini (born 9 November 1913) was an Austrian alpine skier. She competed in the women's combined event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1913 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Austrian female alpine skiers Category:Olympic alpine skiers of Austria Category:Alpine skiers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Vienna
